## Notes

* Using SPNEGO with MIT and gss-ntlmssp is able to use both the Kerberos and NTLM mechs if available
* Defaults to Kerberos
* The 1st token contains the SPNEGO token which includes both mechs and the first Kerberos token
* The 2nd token contains the SPNEGO response wrapping the Kerberos response stating the accepted mech and no MIC
